category: PHP
requires: php
sdesc: "PHP script debugging extension"
ldesc: "The PHP Xdebug extension helps you debugging your script by 
providing a lot of valuable debug information. The debug information 
that Xdebug can provide includes the following:

* stack and function traces in error messages with:
o full parameter display for user defined functions
o function name, file name and line indications
o support for member functions
* memory allocation
* protection for infinite recursions"
